  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to rnnoise</title>

    <para>
      <application>rnnoise</application> is a noise suppression 
      library based on a recurrent neural network.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
